See also [`RangedU64ValueParser`]

# Examples

```rust
let mut cmd = clap::Command::new("raw")
    .arg(
        clap::Arg::new("port")
            .long("port")
            .value_parser(3000..)
            .action(clap::ArgAction::Set)
